telegram bot to control
- wireguard
- adguard home
---
environment: ubuntu 18.04/20.04/22.04, debian 11

install:

wget -O- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/artemionov/vpnbot/master/scripts/init.sh | sh -s YOUR_TELEGRAM_BOT_KEY

---

additional options:

install as service(autoload on start):

bash scripts/install_as_service.sh
